<subSubSection pageId="16" pageNumber="137" type="notes">
<paragraph pageId="16" pageNumber="137">Notes.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="16" pageNumber="137">
Three gatherings were cited in the protologue of 
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Melastomataceae" genus="Barthea" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Barthea cavaleriei" order="Myrtales" pageId="16" pageNumber="137" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="cavaleriei">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="137">Barthea cavaleriei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, viz. Cavalerie 1552, Esquirol 1581 and Esquirol 215, without designation of a type. Two of the syntypes, Esquirol 1581 and 215 were later cited as the types of 
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Melastomataceae" genus="Barthea" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Barthea esquirolii" order="Myrtales" pageId="16" pageNumber="137" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="esquirolii">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="137">Barthea esquirolii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
H. 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Lév">Lev</normalizedToken>
. (1913) and 
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Melastomataceae" genus="Barthea" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Barthea blinii" order="Myrtales" pageId="16" pageNumber="137" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="blinii">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="137">Barthea blinii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
H. 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Lév">Lev</normalizedToken>
. (1913), respectively. 
<bibRefCitation author="Guillaumin, A" editor="Lecomte, MH" journalOrPublisher="2. G. Masson, Paris" pageId="19" pageNumber="140" pagination="864 - 936" refId="B10" refString="Guillaumin, A, 1913. Melastomataceae. In: Lecomte, MH, Gagnepain, F, Eds., Flore Generale de l'Indo-Chine. 2. G. Masson, Paris: 864 - 936" title="Melastomataceae." volumeTitle="Flore Generale de l'Indo-Chine." year="1913">Guillaumin (1913)</bibRefCitation>
transferred 
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Melastomataceae" genus="Barthea" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Barthea cavaleriei" order="Myrtales" pageId="16" pageNumber="137" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="cavaleriei">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="137">Barthea cavaleriei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
to 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Stapf" authorityYear="1892" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Melastomataceae" genus="Fordiophyton" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Fordiophyton" order="Myrtales" pageId="16" pageNumber="137" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="137">Fordiophyton</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
citing only Cavalerie 1552 under the new combination 
<taxonomicName genus="F." lsidName="F. cavaleriei" pageId="16" pageNumber="137" rank="species" species="cavaleriei">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="137">F. cavaleriei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(H. 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Lév">Lev</normalizedToken>
.) Guillaumin. 
<bibRefCitation author="Diels, L" journalOrPublisher="Botanische Jahrbuecher fuer Systematik, Pflanzengeschichte und Pflanzengeographie" pageId="19" pageNumber="140" pagination="97 - 119" refId="B8" refString="Diels, L, 1932. Beitraege zur Kenntnis der Melastomataceen Ostasiens. Botanische Jahrbuecher fuer Systematik, Pflanzengeschichte und Pflanzengeographie 65: 97 - 119" title="Beitraege zur Kenntnis der Melastomataceen Ostasiens." volume="65" year="1932">Diels (1932)</bibRefCitation>
formally designated Cavalerie 1552 as the lectotype and published a new combination 
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Melastomataceae" genus="Bredia" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Bredia cavaleriei" order="Myrtales" pageId="16" pageNumber="137" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="cavaleriei">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="137">Bredia cavaleriei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(H. 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Lév">Lev</normalizedToken>
.) Diels. However, this name is an illegitimate later homonym of 
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Melastomataceae" genus="B." higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="B. cavaleriei" order="Myrtales" pageId="16" pageNumber="137" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="cavaleriei">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="137">B. cavaleriei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
H. 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Lév">Lev</normalizedToken>
. &amp; Vaniot (see Art. 53.1). 
<bibRefCitation author="Chen, C" editor="Wu, ZY" journalOrPublisher="2. Science Press, Beijing" pageId="19" pageNumber="140" pagination="77 - 137" refId="B2" refString="Chen, C, 1979. Melastomataceae. In: Wu, ZY, Ed., Flora Yunnanica, vol. 2. Science Press, Beijing: 77 - 137" title="Melastomataceae." volumeTitle="Flora Yunnanica, vol." year="1979">Chen (1979)</bibRefCitation>
published the replacement name 
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Melastomataceae" genus="B." higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="B. longiradiosa" order="Myrtales" pageId="16" pageNumber="137" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="longiradiosa">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="137">B. longiradiosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
C. Chen for this species, but he did not provide a full reference of the basionym, which makes the name invalid (see Art. 41.1). 
<bibRefCitation author="Chen, C" journalOrPublisher="Science Press, Beijing," pageId="19" pageNumber="140" pagination="135 - 293" refId="B4" refString="Chen, C, 1984b. Melastomataceae. Flora Reipublicae Popularis Sinicae. Science Press, Beijing, 53: 135 - 293" title="Melastomataceae. Flora Reipublicae Popularis Sinicae." volume="53" year="1984 b">Chen (1984b)</bibRefCitation>
subsequently transferred the species to 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Blume" authorityYear="1831" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Melastomataceae" genus="Phyllagathis" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Phyllagathis" order="Myrtales" pageId="16" pageNumber="137" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="137">Phyllagathis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. As the epithet 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="137">cavaleriei</emphasis>
is also not available in 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Blume" authorityYear="1831" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Melastomataceae" genus="Phyllagathis" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Phyllagathis" order="Myrtales" pageId="16" pageNumber="137" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="137">Phyllagathis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, a new name 
<taxonomicName genus="P." lsidName="P. longiradiosa" pageId="16" pageNumber="137" rank="species" species="longiradiosa">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="137">P. longiradiosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
C. Chen was published together with the description of a new variety, 
<taxonomicName genus="P." infraspecific-rank="var." lsidName="P. longiradiosa var. pulchella" pageId="16" pageNumber="137" rank="variety" species="longiradiosa" variety="pulchella">P. longiradiosa var. pulchella</taxonomicName>
C. Chen. There are three effectively published names for this species in 
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Melastomataceae" genus="Bredia" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Bredia" order="Myrtales" pageId="16" pageNumber="137" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="137">Bredia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. With 
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Melastomataceae" genus="B." higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="B. cavaleriei" order="Myrtales" pageId="16" pageNumber="137" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="cavaleriei">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="137">B. cavaleriei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(H. 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Lév">Lev</normalizedToken>
.) Diels illegitimate and 
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Melastomataceae" genus="B." higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="B. longiradiosa" order="Myrtales" pageId="16" pageNumber="137" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="longiradiosa">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="137">B. longiradiosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
C. Chen invalid, the only legitimate name, 
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Melastomataceae" genus="B." higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="B. longiradiosa" order="Myrtales" pageId="16" pageNumber="137" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="longiradiosa">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="137">B. longiradiosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
C. Chen ex Govaerts is adopted as the correct name for this species.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
